ThisForth is a macro-oriented Forth based on Standard (ANS) Forth 94-08-16. 

==== Features ====
* Integrated macro processing 
* Input/output re-assignment 
* Portable implementation 
* Easy extensibility 
* Pinhole optimization 

* http://sal.kachinatech.com/F/1/THISFORTH.html
* Source: ftp://ftp.taygeta.com/pub/Forth/Compilers/native/unix/this4th.tar.gz
* http://www.taygeta.com/forthcomp.html

ThisForth is from WilBaden , to be seen in JeffFox 's Cinema.

